ry factor analysis and the investigation of causal\nlinks. The results obtained in this work have important material implications\nfor the conceptualization of \"religiosity,\" and important methodological\nimplications for the scientific study of religion.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 20 Apr 2017 12:37:15 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 6 Jun 2019 12:56:06 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 11 Jun 2019 12:05:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-06-12"}
